snippet.textDisplay:
I think this season has been the best season of coke studio so far !
I don't think you had so many blockbuster songs in a single season before season 9.
Afreen , Rang , Mann Kunto Maula , Khaki Banda , Baliye , Par Channa , Sab Jag Soye , Jhallaya ，Aaaqa , Dilruba Na Raazi etc etc . The list is long .
This season brought together different music directors  and with them came different sounds .
Rohail Hyatt was no doubt good but Strings  is not bad either  ! Taj dar e haram one of the biggest hits of coke studio was also  produced by Strings .
I as a Fan am excited for the next season  , and this season has definitely raised my expectations !
